text: I seldom rate apps, but this one is special since I really love this app. By simply taping on the screen, you can connect and disconnect the circles. It is so interesting. For those who have not downloaded it, don't hesitate to download it! Although I gave a five star review, there are some tiny issues. The app is actually larger than it says in READ MORE. Ads pop up frequently.  You can try to disconnect with wifi or data, then no more ads will show up. You can also mute the music, if you don't like it.

Good low key brain game. Ads frequency, but more so their sound ruin any experience it's trying to create for the free version. I get needing adds, but are loud obnoxious ads really necessary in a game that is supposed to be relaxing and zen inducing?
